description:
These lightweight shorts have technical features to suit hiking, canoe trips or travelling. A gusseted crotch gives you mobility for stepping over logs on the trail. Lots of pockets keep your snacks and maps within reach and safely tucked away.Stretch nylon fabric is comfortable and durable in urban or backcountry environments.Fabric is quick-drying with a DWR finish.Belt loops, zip fly and a button closure.Gussetted crotch allows unrestricted movement.Jeans-like hand pockets and top stitched rear pockets.1 zippered and 1 envelope cargo pocket provide extra storage.

